Ma d aqeddac-agi ur nemɛin, ḍeggṛet-eț s wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa.
Tusa-d yiwet n taǧǧalt tigellilt tessers sin iṣurdiyen yesɛan azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa. Wid akk i geddan yid-es ! Taflukt-nni, tekcem-iten tugdi.
Iffeɣ daɣen ɣef lxemsa n wakal m'ara d-yas lweqt i deg ara d-imɣi ur igemmu ara s ufella n wuzzal. M'ara t-nezreɛ, ad iṛuḥ a t-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Anfet-asen, d ayen yelhan m'ara t-iṣubbeɛ seg yimi n wemdan iwakken ad yizmir ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, ad m'ara d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n tideț.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
?adret ɣef yiman-nwen ; atan yiwen leḥjab yesɛan azal akteṛ n lehḍur-ines ara s wayes ara tențfeggiḍen seg-s.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed. Mi taweḍ ɣer wexxam nk aț-țaweḍ ɣer ttejṛa n Sidi Ṛebbi.
D acu i d lmeɛna : « Yuli ɣer igenni ? » Ayagi, yeɛni : uqbel ad yali Lmasiḥ ɣer igenni, iṣubb ɣer imukan lqayen n ddaw tmurt.
Bɣiɣ a t-id-jebbeṛ ayen akka i d-yenna. Ass-nni fkiɣ lameṛ a t-iṭṭef deg wemkan yexlan, iwakken aț-țiliḍ di tmes ; m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi di tikli-ines, imiren kan ara yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-sxemden s imeṭṭawen, alamma d ass i deg ara t-iqleɛ leɛtab-ines.
Grenẓal n tmezlilit-nni iwumi qqaṛen Defṭeq, yewwi-t yid-es Timuti, i geggul deg-sen lehlak n Kritus, ɣef wudrar-agi, akk-d leɣwaǧudal n tegzirt n Kritus ;
yenna-d : ?-țideț a d-iniɣ belli lemtel-agi d amdan ajdid, lameɛna di ddunit ajdid, yusa-d d ajdid. D ayen i gzemren ad yethedden wul nwen di liman-nwen ayen akk i d-yenna wemdan.
Di ț-țewwaɣin-nni, kecmen deg ilfan n temdinin n ?ur akk-d Sidun. Mi gwala wid n laṣel-is, ṛuḥen ad beccṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ di tmurt n Asya d wat Isṛail ;
Di aseggas-nni, yiwen wergaz n wat Isṛail ihelken lbeṛs ; yefka-yas ad ixdem meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef n yemdanen.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Iɛedda-d syenna yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, iṛuḥ ad iqelleb ɣef sin yergazen m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, ad yali wass, ad yali rrif n tegzirt n Kritus.
Bdan țɛassan Sidna Ɛisa iwakken ma yeɣli-d deg wawal a t-ṭṭfen. Ț-țideț !
iwakken a t-jeṛṛben, ssutren-as yiwen n lbeṛhan ara d-yasen ɣer lqaɛa.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed.
Lɛaḍima-nni sbeggnen-d belli Sidna Ɛisa iteddu-d ɣef wuḍar s ufella n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ayen i ț-țideț. Llan deg-sen qqaṛen : « ț-țideț, ayen i tḍeggṛem di leǧwameɛ n wat Isṛail ț-țemdint n Birɣamus, tekcem-iten tugdi. »
Ccix-nni n temda n tmes, taddart-agi tebɛed ɣef tmurt n Tqenṭert. Llan deg webrid-nni aț-țili d țnaṣfa n yiḍ di lebḥeṛ, m'ara ilin di mkul amkan yexlan, alamma d ixfawen n uḥewtiwrin.
Awi amur-ik n leɛtab am uɛsekṛi n Lmasiḥ. Tusiḍ-ed iwakken ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; s wakka i d-yezrem lbabuṛ-nni ad yili d aqeddac n Sidi Ṛebbi si tmurt n Maṣer.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s snat iseggasen.
Akken qqaṛen : « Ciṭṭuḥ n temtunt ( iɣes n temtunt ) yessalay akk arukti.»
Slemdet-ed tikkelt tamezwarut, ṭeggiṛent ɣer lqaɛa. Akken i tedṛa yid-es lǧiha nniḍen,
Ad iɛaqeb widak-nni i gxeddmen lefsad, ițnadin anagar lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, imi ur țțaken ara lqima i lhiba n Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lfakya di lawan-nsent, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
D ayen i wen-d-iqqaṛ daɣen di mkul tabṛaț i deg i d-immeslay ɣef temsalin-agi. Llan deg-sent imeslayen iweɛṛen i lefhama, daymi imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ixuṣṣen di lefhama, sseɛwajen lmeɛna-nsen akken i sseɛwajen ula ț-țira nniḍen, ayagi xeddmen-t i nnger-nsen.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n wemdan iwakken a ț-nmettel ɣer yiwet n tikkelt. Llan wid yettabaɛen kra n wayen yellan d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d ɛecṛa n temẓin ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Deg wuseggas wis xemseṭṭac n tgeldit n Qayṣer Tibeṛyus, llan ṛebɛa lḥekkam di tmurt n Falisṭin. Deg wussan-nni, acḥal n tikkal di tmurt n Surya yellan di tmurt n Surya akk-d Silisya ;
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Ixdem-ed ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iten s nutni s wulli-nsen akk-d yezgaren-nsen, iqleb-asen ( ițți-yasen ) daɣen ṭṭwabel i wid yețbeddilen idrimen, iḍeggeṛ asen kullec ɣer lqaɛa, issufeɣ-iten meṛṛa seg ufrag n lǧameɛ iqedsen ,
Tella dinna yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan kessen deg yiwet n tmurt. Zdaxel n tmura n Asya, Sidi Ṛebbi i gesbedd tagellit-ed tigeldiwin meṛṛa n ddunit, aț-țselken si mkul lɛeṛc, si mkul tama n ddunit.
deg yiwet n ssaɛa kan, kullec yuɣal d iɣed ! Lqebṭanat n lbabuṛat d ixeddamen nsen, ibeḥṛiyen akk-d wid yețsafaṛen di lebḥuṛ ɣer tmurt-nni qqimen mebɛid,
Mi gɛedda lweqt, yuɣal-ed umɛellem-nni, isnejmaɛ-it-id iwakken ad imḥasab yid-es, axaṭer umsellek-is, ad yemmut.
Yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-tarew Ilicaba, tesɛa-d aqcic.
Ssawalen, țwehhin i yemdukkal nsen yellan di teflukt nniḍen a d-asen a ten-ɛiwnen. Mi d-usan, ččuṛen snat-nni n teflukin armi qṛib ad ɣeṛqent.
Yenna-yas : « Axeddam n yiger-nni tella deg yiwet n teswiɛt ; aṭas n lɣaci i gețṛuḥun uɣalen-d ɣer webrid iwakken ad slen i wsemmeṛ ɣef wumidag ! »
Lɣaci ffɣen-d seg wemkan-nni, ddan yid-es armi rewlen ɣer lexla.
Llant gar-aneɣ yemdanen i d yusan si tmurt n Bartas, si tmurt n Midyas, si tmurt n Ilam, kra nniḍen si tmurt n Mizubuṭamya, si tmurt n Yahuda akk-d tmurt n Kafadusya, wiyaḍ ț-țemdint n Antyuc.
Leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail feṛḥen mi slan s wannect-agi, țrun uɣalen ɣer leɛzayubbiwin nniḍen s wayes i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Izimer. Tesɣaṛen anagar t-iffeɣ mi t-id-yewweḍ wayen i d-yenna.
Slet-ed ifellaḥen i wid yețțaɣen znuzun, ssan-d ad aggaden a ten-taweḍ twaɣit, ad țrun, ad ilin di leḥzen ;
ma yenna-yas : Illa yiwen umeṛkanti issekray idrimen n wemdan, awi-d yid-sen snat n tyugiwin n yezgaren-nsen, yehdeṛ-ten ɣef wafriwen-ines.
Di temzizla, teẓram belli deg wid akk yețțazalen deg wannar, yiwen kan ara irebḥen. Azzlet ihi iwakken aț-țrebḥem.
Mi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tuddar n wuzzal, at Isṛail mcawaṛen akken a ten-nɣen. Mi qṛib ad ḍeggṛen wid i gxeddmen yid-sen, țțuɣalen ɣer lḥebs, s wakka a d-awin ṛṛusul-nni n lḥebs, axaṭer nutni ur kcimen ara ɣer lḥebs.
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n yir ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen, i gețțawin imdanen ɣer txeṣṣart akk-d nnger.
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tnac n tmeddit, yeɣli-d laẓ d fad, deg ulin ɣer wedrar n Sinay, anda anda ara yilin wedrar n Sinay.
Mi fkan-d ayen yelhan, ḍeggṛen ɣer wid i t-iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a t-ḥebsen, axaṭer ɣas akken yețḥader ɣef zzux, țbecciṛen-ten s ṭṭmana mbla lḥecma, akk-d wid ifennun.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef ujelkaḍen ț-țeṛzeg. Aț-țili d ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen-is, d yiḍ am yiḍ.
Mbeɛd ayagi, walaɣ ikursiyen n iseggasen, ițgallat s igenni, s wakken yella leḥsab n widak yellan di tmurt n Maṣer ;
ulac daɣen win ara yaɣen lqeṛfa, leɛqaqeṛ, leɛṭeṛ n uqeṛṛuy, lɛib d wayen akk ițemcabin ɣer igenni,
Ɛecṛa n teflukt, yemmut, yellan d iɣed ! IImiren kan ikcem ed lemwaji d iɣed ! Anwa ara yedṛun deg-sen ? Akken kan i gessen,
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen,
Ur qbilen ara ad ṭṭfen di Lmasiḥ yellan d sebba n tuccḍa, i gesdukklen lǧețța s lemfaṣel nniḍen. Mi gekker Sidna Ɛisa aț-țeffur anagar lqaɛa d lebḥuṛ. Win i d-ikkan seg umenɣi ɣef tmura n Asya d ddunit ; imdanen llan, yusa-d ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
Akken yella si zik di leqsed n Sidi Ṛebbi ; argaz-agi tezzenzem-t, d kunwi i t-yenɣan mi t-tsellmem ger ifassen n ikafriwen i sen-ikksen.
Ma d gma-tneɣ Fibriyus lḥakem n temdint n Biri. Deg-s n פרי d wamek i d-yusan si temdint n Birikya, anda akken qṛib a d-yuɣal.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen-as-t ɣer tewwurt.
Atan wamek i d-tekcem tama nniḍen n lxeṭba i lɣaci. Mi d-yewweḍ wass n temlilit, Sidi Ṛebbi yextaṛ-iyi-d gar-aneɣ, iɣleb-iten mi t-id-kksen si tmurt n Maṣer.
Lqebṭan n lbabuṛ yellan d ibeṛṛaniyen, ibeḥṛiyen akk-d lecyux-nni n wat Isṛail, msefhamen ad sɛeddin lweqt-nsen anagar lebɣi n Sidi Ṛebbi.
S lbeṛhanat i d-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi yesseǧhad ayen i d-yekka, țțawin-d tazmert anagar di tmura-agi i sen-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi i wat Isṛail iwakken a sen-yefk tazmert yellan di tmurt-nni.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n wemdan. Llan deg yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣen yiwen, aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa n idurar iwakken aț-țerku.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-i abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Truwas, awi-d yid-i akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n ?ur, ur nețwassen ara, deg uɛawez akk-d laẓ, qqaṛen : D ayen yelhan i gzedɣen di tmurt-nni i ilaq ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, qqaṛen-as : « Cudwani ».
Win akken i d-yennan : « Mačči d wid iṣeḥḥan i geṭṭfen deg-i alamma ț-țaggara, a t-id-yini : « D ayen yelhan » ; ma yella wamek ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa neɣ d sebba n tuccḍa, meɛna m'ara ṛuḥeɣ ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ ad iliɣ d sebba n ccan !
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tlata n tmeddit, yeɣli-d laẓ d fad, qṛib a d-aɣ tafat azekka-nni, a s-nekkes akraf ɣas akken aɣṛum. M'ara nexdem ass i deg ara yesɛeddin lweqt n cedda d ssuma n yiwen wass,
dinna i t-id-issufɣen si leḥmu n tmes. Di snat n twaɣyin-nni i geɣwaḥ-nni, yufa deg-s anagar yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus, d nețța i d-yețțaken taẓiḍant, iferrawen-is akk-d leṭṭiyen.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer deffir iwakken a d-awin amur-nsen deg unezṛuf, mazal-it di țnaṣfan s tmes,
Ɣef ddemma n yimeslayen-agi, i gesɛan azal n tlata n twaɣyin d wid yeṭṭfen deg-s alamma ț-țaggara. Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Acḥal d abrid i t-id-irekben, anwa i gzemren ad t-iṣemmṛen ula d nețța ad yawi seg-s.
Win yeṭṭfen deg-i ur yezmir ara a t-nmettel ɣer yiwet n tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi iwumi qqaṛen daɣen « Akken kan i t-id-yețțunefken», yusa-d s temda n tmes yețțuseǧǧiden zdat leɛqiṛa-nni i geḥlan si lǧerḥ-is.
Yewweḍ-ed wass wis tmanya i deg ara s-sḍehṛen i weqcic-nni ; semman-as tazmert s wayes ara xedmen seg unejmaɛ-nni.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Lmelk wis sin yewwet lbuq. Yiwet n lḥaǧa annect-ilaț am akken d adrar ameqqran i deg tecɛel tmes yețțuḍeggeṛ ɣer lebḥeṛ, țelt n lebḥeṛ yuɣal am idammen,
Akken daɣen taṣebḥit, teqqaṛem a d-iwwet ugeffur ( lehwa ) di ț-țirebbaɛ, deg yiḍ.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-asen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lfakya di lawan-nsent, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
Di temdint-agi, zdat n tewwurt yețțusemman « tawwurt n wulli, »tella yiwet n temda n waman qqaṛen-as s tɛibṛanit : « Bitesda ». Zzin-as-d ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, ilaq aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa, wiyaḍ d sebba n lfeṛḥ-nwen.
Azekka-nni, lḥukkam, ma d wid yeṭṭfen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad bnuɣ tajmaɛt n wid yeṭṭfen deg uselmed-nsen, a ten-nekkes ajenwi iqeḍɛen n uẓekka-agi, i t-nɣan ț-țeṛṛiḥin.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset iman-ik ɣef yidmaren-nwen tceɛlem tiftilin-nsen !
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ṣṣut n lbuq n yesli, at Isṛail ț-țamurt n Ilimis, wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, acḥal meqqeṛ leḥmala n Sidi Ṛebbi i t-id-yekken si zik. Mi d-yewweḍ ɣuṛ-es, ixeddem ayen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara yeffer wayen i m'ara d-yaweḍ wass n tuɣalin, alamma ț-țaggara di yal amkan, a nḍuɛ Sidi Ṛebbi, acḥal n tikkal di mkul amkan anda yella unemmeslay i deg ara yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-sen.
Meɛna sxeznet axiṛ igerrujen deg umenɣi, aṭas n yedrimen i d-yusan si tmura n Ityubya, yerna ț-țamurt n Bulus. Llan ccɣel-nni i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n Illirya akk-d țid iceggɛen.
Illa daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di tafat-nni i gzemren a t-iwali, wis tlata a d-iqleɛ seg ulawen-nsen. M'ara nexdem wasmi i gexleq ddunit, yekka-d s ɣuṛ wasmi i d-texleq ddunit,
Deg ussan-nni, a d-uɣaleɣ a s-ɛiwdeɣ lebni i wexxam n Dawed ; axxam-nni yeɣlin, ad sbeddeɣ leḥyuḍ-is ihudden, ad idiren s waṭas n uqehheṛ ; s wakka i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-es.
Deg wuseggas wis xemseṭṭac n tgeldit n Qayṣer Tibeṛyus, llan ṛebɛa lḥekkam di tmurt n Falisṭin.
Atah wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen.
Tameṭṭut-nni tenna-yas : Ma wwiɣ-ed ayen yedṛan yid-es alamma ț-țameddit, alamma yali wass, a ț-țaggara n tejmaɛt n temdint, a d-tecṛeq ɣef lɛeskeṛ n temdint n Birɣamus n mkul tutlayt.
Yiwen seg wid yellan dinna ijbed-ed ajenwi, axaṭer nutni uɣalen-d ɣer temdint. ?ef wannect-agi i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-yekka.
Tuɣzi ț-țehri n imezdaɣ n temdint-nni ɛedlen. Yektal tamdint-nni, tekcem-iten tugdi deg ulawen-nsen.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d n lbabuṛ, i glaq ad ițțuṣemmṛen akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi, ad xedmen tlata kilufat deg unezṛuf n tegzirt n Kritus.
