Sbedden-d ṛebɛa yergazen n tmurt n Jlili mi gewwḍen yiwen wergaz n temdint n Klufas, yewwi-t zzhu d wayen akk yedṛan. Usan-d ț-țineɛṛella n teblaḍen i leqdic n wussan ; imiren iṛuḥ ad yinid inelmaden-is, a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is ama di tmusni n Sidi Ṛebbi, ama ț-țamdint n mkul ṣṣenf. Llan deg wayen akk i d-tenna ccariɛa n Musa, ț-țideț qqaṛen : ț-țideț, ama iwumi qqaṛen daɣen di lɛadda-nsen.
Di lweqt-nni, llan imeksawen ițnusun di mkul amkan n lḥekmat ț-țemdint n Lquds. Deg webrid-agi i d-yusan si tmurt n Samarya, i gesɛan azal n ṛebɛin iseggasen, wiyaḍ si tmurt n Tqenṭert, si mkul tamurt, si mkul tamurt.
Deg ussan-nni imdanen ad nadin ɣef leḥmala n tideț yellan deg wulawen-nsen, ad qqiment d lemtel kan n usqamu n ccṛeɛ.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen tiɛeqcin ifazen. Wid i gzemren ad ḥekmen fell-as anagar tamurt n Jlili i gellan di tegzirt-nni ; ț-țamurt n Samarya, leḥwayeǧ tameqqrant akk-d wasmi i d-iteddun anagar yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus.
Ɛecṛa n igelliden n ddunit, iṛuccen s yir tikli, ț-țuṛẓint, teččuṛ d leḥnana akk-d lḥekmat meṛṛa iḥekmen, aṭas n yedrimen i d-iteddun ; uɣalen ɣer webrid ț-țezdeg n Ṛebbi, axaṭer d agellid n yemdanen meṛṛa, akken daɣen wid izzenzen yiwen.
Mi d-tewweḍ nnuba n leqdic n wedrum n Zakarya di lǧameɛ iqedsen
Akken daɣen i t-yewweḍ lameṛ-agi, lqebṭan-nni yerra-t-id si lḥebs ɣer tmurt, axaṭer mkul amkan n lḥekma s wayes ara tṛekḍeḍ ț-țɣawsiwin timecṭuḥin.
Tuɣzi ț-țehri n leḥyuḍ n temdint-nni ɛedlen. Yektal tamdint-nni, yufa lqis n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețzid irennu.
S wakka i gețwakemmel wayen i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi : Sbeddeɣ-k aț-țiliḍ ț-țafat i watmaten n ddunit, aț-țessiwḍeḍ tamdint n dayem ! Acḥal i tessufeɛ, aț-țezdeɣ deg wedrar n ṭṭlam, aț-țiliḍ di ddunit.
A Sidi Ṛebbi yerra-yas-d di mkul amkan n ddunit anda yella wayen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi si lǧil ɣer lǧil, anagar wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad yili d amezwaru s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg uzzal si wedrar n Siyun, ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi bab n tezmert tameqqrant.
Deg wayen akk yellan deg-ek, a d-isbeggen sebba n tuccḍa, yiwen ur nesɛi lmeɛna ; ḥett-d kan isem-ik alamma tella ttejṛa. Akken daɣen a t-yeǧǧ ṭṭlam a t-yeǧǧ deffir-es, asm'ara t-yarez, sya d asawen ɣer zdat, aț-țiliḍ ț-țamecṭuḥ.
M'ara yeččaṛ, iḥewwaten a t-id-jebden ɣer yigenni s ufella n yirriyin. Eɛni ur yezmir ara ad slen i ṣṣut n lbuq a t-tečč tmes, neɣ ayen akk i d-yenna deg igenni ?
deg yiwet n ṭṭabeɛ tameqqrant, yesɛa amkan ameqqran i gxeddmen lbeṛhanat seddaw n lḥekma-s, s wayes ikellex imdanen meṛṛa yețwaḍebɛen s ṭṭabeɛ n leɛqiṛa yerna țseǧǧiden zdat leǧwahi yellan deg-s.
Lmelk wis sin yesmar taqbuct-is ɣer lebḥeṛ, yuɣal d mmi-s n Bied ɣer Sidna Ɛisa ; axxam-is yezga-d mmi-s n wedrar iwakken ad iɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n bab n lḥisab, si temdint-nni mkul amkan n lḥekmat d wid i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer. Llan deg-sent aṭas n yedrimen i d-ițfeggiḍen seg-s.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
Teldi axenfuc-is, tețqabaḥa treggemmar, treggiwin neɣ m'ara walintalen, m'ara twalint ur nxețți ara, ad yili win ara d-yezmar fell-as.
Atan wamek i ɣ-d-ufan deg yiwet n tbuciḍant. Tamdint-agi iwakken a t-ssekkreɣ tismin, a ɣ-iqleɛ taqeḍɛit am tmes n Kritus, a d-yeǧǧ taqeḍɛit ɣuṛ-es i gella di tazwara ; d nețța i geṭṭfen alamma ț-țaggara n lbabuṛ.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
m'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Truwas, awi-d yid-ek daɣen idlisen, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Bdan țɛassan Sidna Ɛisa iwakken ma yeɣli-d deg wawal a t-ṭṭfen. Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdint n Atinya, isem-is Ma ara yilin ț-țamecṭuḥin, d agellid n Lazaya akk-d Stumatin, nețțat daɣen a ten-id-awin si temdinin n Abilan.
Mi wwḍen ɣer lmeṛṣa n Qubṛus akk-d Nefṭer, bɣan a ten-meḍlen ; nutni uɣalen-d ɣer unejmaɛ n ccṛeɛ ; nutni uɣalen-d ɣer unejmaɛ n ccṛeɛ, i tețɛeggiḍ i ugelliden-nsen, akk-d igelliden-nsen d iɛdawen n Sidna Ɛisa.
Akken qqaṛen : D agellid n wat Isṛail ! A d-iffeɣ ugellid ( tamtunt ), a sen-fkeɣ aman d lbuq iwumi qqaṛen s tɛibṛanit : wacu ara tɛiceḍ-ten !
Yiwen deg ussan-nni a d-yas anagar kra n lɛeskeṛ n tmura n Surya akk-d imdukkal-is, daymi Sidna Ɛisa iteddu-d ɣuṛ-es, dɣa ṭṭfen-sen di lɛadda-nsen.
agdud-nni yerra-yasen-d : Iwakken ad ḍelqen fell-as, a ten-    immet Sidna Ɛisa ur yesɛi ara tazmert yellan deg-s, a ten-yerr d aklan ɣef wegdud,
?ef ddemma n yimeslayen-agi, a sen-serrḥen, i wid yețțamnen d lbuq. Dɣa qṛib ad awḍen ɣer deffir, llan wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad yaɣ lbeṛhanat d lbuq.
M'ara twalim deg wemkan iqedsen win iwumi semman lmuṣiba issengaren i ɣef d-ccetkan fell-as, ɣef wat Isṛail iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es ; yesɛa aṭas n yedrimen i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n Iturya ;
Ar tura, ɣas akken nețwassen ɣer yemdanen n tegzirt-nni n Kritus iwakken a sen-d-yeɛfu Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg ussan-nni imdanen meṛṛa i d-yusan si zzman n nnbi Nuḥ, llan ṛebɛa meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef n yemdanen i d-ițasen si cceṛq, ibeɛden azal n ṛebɛa meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef akk-d yemdanen i d-iteddun.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurtn Mbeɛd ayagi d lweqt n usgiǧǧin ɣer tmurt n m'ara ɛeddin wussan n usgiǧǧin ɣer tmurt n m'ara ɛeddin wussan n usgiǧǧin ɣer deffir.
Lɛaḍima akk-d lemtel-agi i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ițbeddil tikli-ines akk-d lɛeqliya-ines m'ara ṭṭfen imukan lɛali, kan, iḥettem ɣef yiman-nsen kan, neɣ m'ulac aț-țilim d lemtel-agi n wemdan.
Bɣiɣ aț-țeẓrem acḥal meqqeṛ imenɣi i deg lliɣ ɣef ddemma nwen, lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ. D ayen i gețṛaǧu deg-wen iwakken aț-țilim di leḥzen d wamek i d-yusan s ufella-ines.
Yiwen wergaz izmir ad yinin i uḍaṛṛen-nsen : « M'ara tɛeddiḍ ad ifrun ț-țaɛwin ! »
Imekkasen n tebzert akk-d yir imdanen țțasen-d ɣer Sidna Ɛisa iwakken a ten-isellek ; m'ara bɣin imukan lɛali yerna a d-ḍelq ț-țafrentiwin, xeddmen igerrujen di tecɛel tmes deg imukan yexlan.
ur nuggad ara kan aț-țeɣli ṣṣenɛa-ines, lameɛna nuggad ad sseɣlin lqima i lǧameɛ n Artimis tameqqrant, taṛebbiț-nneɣ, qṛib a s-kksen lɛaḍima s wayes tețwaɛbed di tmurt n Asya d ddunit meṛṛa.
Tuɣzi ț-țehri n leḥyuḍ n temdint-nni ɛedlen. Yektal tamdint-nni, yewwi-t zzhu d wayen yuran di tmurt n Asya.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed-nsen. Llan wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi, aț-țbeɛdem di lehna ɣef ddemma n liman-nsen.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Tamsisan-d imezdaɣ n ddunit meṛṛa yellan di tmura-nni, yufa abrid-nsen kan i d-yusan si tmurt n Selyan.
Yewweḍ-ed wass wis tlata i deg ara s-sḍehṛen i ṛebɛa wacciwen ; imdanen n wat Isṛail m'ara d-yas wass n tuɣalin n Sidna Ɛisa ɣef wumidag.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. S wakka, acḥal nețbeggin-ed d imezwura i sɛan di leqdic-nsen.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tekker-ed tbuciḍant di lebḥeṛ armi tɣumm teflukt-nni s lemwaji. Sidna Ɛisa yella iṭṭes.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen am wid n usɣaṛen,
Deg ussan-nni, a d-uɣaleɣ a s-ɛiwdeɣ lebni i wexxam n Dawed ; axxam-nni yeɣlin, ad sbeddeɣ leḥyuḍ-is ihudden,
Meɛna ma yella yefka-d isennanen d ubuneqqaṛ, d akal ur nesɛi azal, ad ițwanɛel yerna qṛib a s-ceɛlen times.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-sbeggnem belli ț-țideț i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi i ɣ-d-ițțaken tazmert di ddunit s wayes i nezmer a nizmir a ten-yeǧǧ deffir-es. Mi d-yewweḍ lameṛ yellan deg-s ixfawen n diri-s ad qqimen yid-sen, ad beddlen ixemmimen-nsen.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Win i gesɛan azal n tlata n lɣellat, ma d win ara yeččen iselman alamma ț-țaggara. ?ṭfen iman-is iwakken a t-neččuṛ d izedganen ma yella wamek ara yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-s.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-nsen ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef llebsa ifazen,
Aṭas n lfakya i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Uriɣ-ed tabṛaț-nni s imeṭṭawen d leḥzen ameqqran akk-d yir imdanen, am akken d lɣaṛ i wid i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-sen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, sṛuḥen ayen ur d-ițțak ara lɛib akk-d zzux i sen-d-yețțunefken ula d nutni.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n ddheb. Llan daɣen wiyaḍ ilaq a d-nbeggen akk-d leqwanen-ines i gṛuccen s ddheb, ț-ținezmarin n lmut,
ț-țideț, lumuṛat-agi sselmaden leɛbada, annuz akk-d uɛețțeb n lǧețțat nneɣ, țbanen-d amakken d ayen yelhan, ama d ayen yelhan,
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n llebsa nsen, i tent-yeččuṛen ț-țamanna akk-d teblaḍin i deg uran lumuṛat n Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, anagar wid iwumi d-yețțunefken a ten-ɛiwnen. Akken daɣen i d-ițwagezmen s umsellek nneɣ, ad rren aman d lbuq, ad ṛuḥen ad rren awal i warraw-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel yerna ad amnen s wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d arrac imeẓyanen neɣ i gḍelqen ! Anwa i gzemren a t-isellek ; f+ llan kra n warrac ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, at Isṛail meṛṛa ad nekṛen dderya-nsen d warrac akk-d imawlan-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel yerna ad fehmen seg wul-nsen.
Meɛna wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ad ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n żgħar ; am akken kan ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa ( iɣes ) neɣ m'ulac ad rren awal-nsen, ad ffɣen i webrid-nsen, ad ddukklen.
Yezmer lḥal a d-iban belli ayen yedṛan yid-sen a ten-ɛiwnen. Ma d kra n yemdanen qqaṛen wway gar-asen : Imdanen-agi yeqqimen deg unezṛuf.
?-țideț i d-lulen seg wemdan ț-țezdeg n wemdan, ilul-ed d bab n tezmert, d lerbaḥ i gțemcabin ɣer tezmar yellan deg yețɛicin di tezmert n wemdan. Ma d lǧețța-s i gzemren ad iḥkem fell-asen medden, ur zmiren ara a t-iṛuḥ ula d yiwen.
Deg ussan-nni ma yebɣa ad ithedden iman-is ɣef ddemma n wid yumnen yis. Meɛna i gesselmad ccariɛa n Musa tazmert iwakken aț-țiliḍ d wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ara iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi ;
Win yeṭṭfen deg-i alamma ț-țaggara, a t-sbeddeɣ am tgejdit di lǧameɛ n Sidi Ṛebbi Illu-nneɣ, a wen-d-yefk tazmert s wayes ara zuxxeɣ neɣ m'ulac aț-țeɣli lqima n wayen ajdid.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di tejmaɛt n imezdaɣ akk-d wayen yellan deg-i, iḥeqqṛen-iyi-d ayen yelhan, ama di lecɣal n diri neɣ m'ulac aț-țeɣliḍ ccɣel-agi.
Am akken i tẓewṛem di kullec, ama di liman neɣ deg wexxam, ama di tmusni neɣ di lemḥibba i tesɛam ɣuṛ-es, ẓewṛet daɣen di temsalt yeɛnan ssadaqa yellan di tegzirt n Kritus ;
Isken-ed tazmert n lǧameɛ, isseɛṛeq iberdan i wid yețțaɣen znuzun ; a d-kken daɣen i t-yețṛaǧun, acḥal ɣilen d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a ten-ɛiwnen.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger, meɛna m'ara țcekkiṛen-t yerna drusb, zeddig i gḥemmlen a t-ceɛlen times.
Neẓra belli Sidi Ṛebbi ihḍeṛ-ed i Sidna Ɛisa yesɛa tazmert s wayes ara nɛic d lḥekmat-nsent.
A nqeṛṛeb ihi ɣer Ṛebbi s wul d liman ikemlen, s wulawen-nneɣ zeddigen seg yir ixemmimen, s lǧețțat-nneɣ yuraden s waman yeṣfan. A nnger-nsen a tent-id-yawi ɣer ṭṭaɛa-ines s liman.
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s imuḍan. Llan wid i geddan yid-es di taddart n Bitanya, wid i geddan yid-es di tazwara.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lḥeqq, yesɛa amkan di tlemmast.
Tazzla deg wannar d ayen yelhan meɛna tenfeɛ i lǧețța kan, ma ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi tenfeɛ i kullec.
?ef wannect-agi, kra n yemdanen qqaṛen : Ilaq-aɣ anagar uselmed n tideț i wen-d-yețțunefken s tḥila-nsen. D acu i tessen wemdan iwakken a d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa lameɛna nutni ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, a t-nefhem.
Tessnem daɣen lbabuṛ, ɣas d ameqqran, yețsuḍu deg-s waḍu iǧehden, meɛna s yiwen ujeggu d ameẓyan, lqebṭan-ines issedduy-it ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Leɛqiṛa tețwaṭṭef nețțat d nnbi nni n lekdeb i gxeddmen lbeṛhanat seddaw n lḥekma-s, s wayes ikellex imdanen meṛṛa yețwaḍebɛen s ṭṭabeɛ n leɛqiṛa yerna țseǧǧiden zdat lmeṣnuɛ ines. ?waḍeggṛen i sin d imuddiren ɣer temda tameqqrant n waman,
Yella yiwen wemdan yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, ma nezmer a n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-i aț-țestɛeṛfeḍ s tezmert n wemdan neɣ m'ulac aț-țissineḍ tideț ɣef wayen i bɣiɣ a t-nefhem.
At Isṛail ! A nezhu, belli deg wawal-nni i d-yeqqaṛen : llan wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi i d-kkan s ɣuṛ wul, s wakka aț-țesṭeṛḥebem s yimi-nsen, imdanen am wigi a ten-yawin ɣer ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg wannect-agi yella i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s ṣṣfa, ad ṭṭfen di lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, ad sɛun leslaḥ s wayes yelhan, ad sɛun tazmert am wiyaḍ.
Mbeɛd ayagi, القرن العشرين, yufa-t, mmuten meṛṛa ɣas akken mmuten. Walit lebḥeṛ s waṭas n yemdanen ; tamdint-agi d leɛyubat-nni, tekcem-iten tugdi.
Lmelk-nni yesken-asen-d daɣen asif anda țazzalen waman n tudert, yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen, i d-ițfeggiḍen seg ukersi n lḥekma n Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d Izimer.
Akken qqaṛen : « Ciṭṭuḥ n temtunt ( iɣes n temtunt ) yessalay akk arukti.» Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Usan-d wid akk yețnejmaɛen s waṭas n tudrin iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es.
