Di tmurt n Misya, tella yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d wid i d-yusan si tmurt n Bartas, wwḍent-ed ɣer dinna yiwen wemkan n Libya, widak-nni nevan d iselman ( lḥut ).
