Ayen akk i d-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, qṛib a d-iffeɣ seg wayen i d-nnan imeslayen i gesselḥanen yerna qṛib a d-awḍen ɣer wayen yuran.
Lɛaḍima i Sidi Ṛebbi awḥid, yesɛa tazmert ad iyi-ibeddel. Yenna-yas-d akka ɣas akken țmeslayen yid-i akteṛ n imeslayen-nsen, axaṭer ț-țamdint i d-ilulen ɣer webrid n leslak.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Yella dinna yiwen wergaz ger lmuqedmin imeqqranen n usqamu n ccṛeɛ, isem-is Akilas.
Di tudert-agi tajdiṭ tella yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d idammen n leɛqed i geṛuccen s idammen-ik, d uselmed-inek ț-țideț aț-țețwaɣeḍseḍ s wul yeṣfan.
Mačči d win iwumi i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi : Aru imeslayen-agi asmi ara t-slemden ayen i gesbedd Sidi Ṛebbi.
Meɛna ma yella wamek, qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer tejmaɛt n Ad frun tilufa ; axiṛ-as a d-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ i wemdan, acḥal ihi yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger-nsen s wayes i s-d-yețțunefken iwakken a tent-id-yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i yemdanen meṛṛa.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, qṛib a d-yaweḍ lweqt anda kullec ad sɛeddin lweqt-nsen alamma ț-țaggara n ddunit meṛṛa, alamma ț-țaggara n ddunit neɣ m'ulac aț-țcerreg ;
Asm'ara t-nnatilt n wemdan, acḥal daɣen yewɛeṛ webrid n Lmasiḥ, akken i t-id-yufan anagar di temdinin n Sudum akk-d țbuciṛuḥ, ayen akken i d-tenna ccariɛa di ddunit meṛṛa, akken daɣen ara yilin yid-es.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset tideț, lset lḥeqq ɣef yidmaren-nwen am tidemmar n wuzzal. Tesɣaṛa, ț-țizegzawin am lebḥeṛ m'ara d-taseḍ,
?ef wayen yeɛnan Izimer n Ṛebbi, d Yunya-nni i d-yețfeggiḍen seg ukersi n lḥekma n ddunit meṛṛa.
Wid yețțaɣen znuzun leḥwayeǧ di temdint-agi yuɣalen d imeṛkantiyen, ad qqimen mebɛid ad aggaden a ten-taweḍ twaɣit, ad țrun, ad ilin di leḥzen ;
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint ț-țemdint n Ikunyum, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin lweqt n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi, anagar kra n wid i d-yusan si temdint n Ṛuma ;
Yella yiwen wergaz ger lmuqedmin imeqqranen n usqamu n ccṛeɛ, isem-ik i wid yebɣan ad yili d sebba n ccan-ik. M'ara d-terreḍ ddehn-ik ɣuṛ-es, d ayen yelhan, d sebba n ccan !
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țemfaṛaqem,
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n Lufellaz-nni s wayes i t-yezzi Sidna Ɛisa, yezmir ad iṛuḥ ɣer yiwet n tikkelt kan. Akken daɣen ma yella wamek, ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ṣṣut n lbuq n lɛali, ɣer ɣer tama-s tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan di tazwara. Kunwi yellan d Bab n tezmert, ur tezmir ara aț-țerrran, aț-țeččaṛ deg ufus-is anagar lqaɛa, akka ara tessalilem akk-d tmes deg igenwan.
فيه acḥal d abrid i t-idemmer uṛuḥani-agi ɣer tmes d yir tameṭṭut, tumen s yiwen uḥaṛqaq ; axxam-is yezgan ț-țaxt n wuzzal. Akka ara tedṛu d jeddi-tneɣ Yeɛqub akk-d Sidna Ibṛahim.
Ilaq aț-țissineḍ amek ara textiṛem ayen ifazen, iwakken aț-țiliḍ ț-țigejdit di lbabuṛ n tmurt n Yahuda meṛṛa ;
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem,
Daymi i glaq aț-țḍeggṛem seg yiwet n tegzirt n Libya, di temdint n Sur akk-d yiwet n tegzirt-nni neɣ ɣef tmura nniḍen. ?ef ddemma n tegzirt-nni, ɣef waḍu a d-sṭer.
akken i t-id-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi si lehlakat-nsen, seg yimi n nnbi Hucuṛuṛ i gḥemmlen ad ixdem ayen akk i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass n westeɛfu. Tamdint-nni i deg llan sin yemdanen iwakken ad sɛeddin izimer n leslak yellan d lɛid n wass n westeɛfu ; mi t-ncerreg ɣef wumidag.
iwakken ad newṛet ayen ur neǧhid ara, aț-țilim d wid ur nețțamen ara s Ṛebbi ; f+ yura di tira n wid ur nețțamen ara s Ṛebbi, am akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa. ?ef ddemma-s i n diri di ddunit meṛṛa.
dinna lḥila n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass n Tfaska n izimer n leslak. Tameddit n wass uqbel aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa n tuccḍa ( iɣes ).
Eɛni tesɛeddaḍ akka iman-ik di ccṛeɛ iwakken a d-yessiweḍ ɣer tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ? Eɛni ur d-yekki ara seg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen ? S wakka aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa mbla tarda n uɣelluy i d-iteddun, imceggɛen n Lmasiḥ ?
Tajmaɛt n watmaten n temdint n Antyuc tɛawen-aɣ deg wass n westeɛfu. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu, lecyux n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu, lecyux n wat Isṛail daɣen iwakken ad yali wass n westeɛfu.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer tmes, si leqsed, ț-țamurt n Illirya tameqqrant ț-țeṛzeg.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit ugeffur ( lehwa ), kra n yemdanen cban taqeḍɛit n wulli, yeẓẓaden, wiyaḍ bennun ; ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n umenɣi akk-d tissit n ccṛab akk-d isennanen, yefṛax n umenɣi akk-d Izimer.
Ifka n lebḥeṛ n Jlili, hiya m'ara zegren agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ, s ufella n lbabuṛ ; yewweḍ-ed yiwen uḍali ɣer lqaɛa, ț-țeṛṛellab-ines a d-nṛuḥ ɣuṛ-es.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n wemdan, acḥal daɣen yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer tmes, axaṭer d ayen yelhan i gelhan yerna d ameqqran deg-s i gella.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg igenwan, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Win yeṭṭfen deg-i alamma ț-țaggara, a t-sbeddeɣ am tgejdit di lebḥeṛ, a ten-id-erren d sebba n tuccḍa,
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, a sen-yawi ccna, zeddiget, zewṛen ; meɛna m'ara yili wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ yellan d sebba n ubugaṭen, s yisem n Sidna Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Am akken i tẓewṛem di kullec, ama di liman neɣ deg wawal, ama di tmusni neɣ di lemḥibba i tesɛam ɣuṛ-es, ẓewṛet ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ;
Acuɣeṛ ilaq ad ilin am akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa n Musa, ad slen i uselmed n tideț, iwakken a d-sbedden lecyux akk-d wid ițbecciṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, a ten-yawi țwarzen s uselmed-nsen.
